d 👀", "authorName": "MJ Capital", "authorUsername": "MJCapital_", "authorAvatar": "https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/2071432155649933312/2c5nDxTH_normal.jpg", "authorFollowers": 17, "authorVerified": true, "likeCount": 4, "retweetCount": 1, "replyCount": 0, "quoteCount": 0, "viewCount": 34, "bookmarkCount": 0, "createdAt": "2026-07-10T23:03:57+00:00", "hashtags": [], "isRetweet": false, "url": "https://x.com/MJCapital_/status/2075717692393419205"}, {"id": "2075616685717852432", "text": "$META. again. 🟢\n\nswung another one, went to bed, woke up +630%.\n\nthe timeline’s still catching up to what our members already booked. free right now, next setup’s on the board 👀 https://t.co/0KQnFp8JGs", "authorName": "MJ Capital", "authorUsername": "MJCapital_", "authorAvatar": "https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/2071432155649933312/2c5nDxTH_normal.jpg", "authorFollowers": 17, "authorVerified": true, "likeCount": 5, "retweetCount": 1, "replyCount": 0, "quoteCount": 0, "viewCount": 40, "bookmarkCount": 0, "createdAt": "2026-07-10T16:22:35+00:00", "hashtags": [], "isRetweet": false, "url": "https://x.com/MJCapital_/status/2075616685717852432"}, {"id": "2075408750630801528", "text": "While everyone’s just now tweeting about $META 👀\n\nOur members were already in and out. +377% 🟢\n\nBeing early is the whole edge. free right now, next setup’s already on the board. https://t.co/qMCOy6xVM9", "authorName": "MJ Capital", "authorUsername": "MJCapital_", "authorAvatar": "https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/2071432155649933312/2c5nDxTH_normal.jpg", "authorFollowers": 17, "authorVerified": true, "likeCount": 5, "retweetCount": 1, "replyCount": 0, "quoteCount": 0, "viewCount": 64, "bookmarkCount": 0, "createdAt": "2026-07-10T02:36:20+00:00", "hashtags": [], "isRetweet": false, "url": "https://x.com/MJCapital_/status/2075408750630801528"}, {"id": "2072404511835279538", "text": "Today in the group👇\nWe actually lost more trades than we won and it was still a big green day\n\nWinners: GLD +300%, SNDK +115%. Losers: every single one under -10%\n\nThat’s the whole game right there, keep the losses tiny, let the winners run and yeah, all of it was called free 😏 https://t.co/g4SpK5Ak4g", "authorName": "MJ Capital", "authorUsername": "MJCapital_", "authorAvatar": "https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/2071432155649933312/2c5nDxTH_normal.jpg", "authorFollowers": 17, "authorVerified": true, "likeCount": 4, "retweetCount": 0, "replyCount": 0, "quoteCount": 0, "viewCount": 47, "bookmarkCount": 0, "createdAt": "2026-07-01T19:38:33+00:00", "hashtags": [], "isRetweet": false, "url": "https://x.com/MJCapital_/status/2072404511835279538"}, {"id": "2072075069799497933", "text": "Dropped this alert free in the group yesterday👇 \nToday it’s almost in the money and already printing for everyone who took it\n\nDid I mention it’s all free right now? 😏 https://t.co/Y8pttroYNn", "authorName": "MJ Capital", "authorUsername": "MJCapital_", "authorAvatar": "https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/2071432155649933312/2c5nDxTH_normal.jpg", "authorFollowers": 17, "authorVerified": true, "likeCount": 5, "retweetCount": 0, "replyCount": 0, "quoteCount": 0, "viewCount": 39, "bookmarkCount": 0, "createdAt": "2026-06-30T21:49:28+00:00", "hashtags": [], "isRetweet": false, "url": "https://x.com/MJCapital_/status/2072075069799497933"}, {"id": "2071572740604149791", "text": "Last week in the group — all of it, wins and losses.\n\nWe post the reds too, because anybody can show you a green week. Best was XSP +221%, worst was RDDT −44%. That’s what real trading actually looks like.\n\nStill free while we build it. Lock in in before it goes paid https://t.co/oGLqbbgbQj", "authorName": "MJ Capital", "authorUsername": "MJCapital_", "authorAvatar": "https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/2071432155649933312/2c5nDxTH_normal.jpg", "authorFollowers": 17, "authorVerified": true, "likeCount": 5, "retweetCount": 1, "replyCount": 0, "quoteCount": 0, "viewCount": 47, "bookmarkCount": 0, "createdAt": "2026-